et , men systemet fungerer if\u00f8lge NRK ikke optimalt."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "2704fd75ee1208483ea3370e754e89bf6e9cb6c864ce8ddba361cf17fef4e0ee"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-03-05T06:57:40.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Rennebu kommune fulgte ikke opp pasienten godt nok."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11446349.ece/3vk0is/ALTERNATES/w980-default/20150820_212410.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/7a0fd1936996f82bf01c5517ab66a0696a183830.jpg?598bf071"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Fylkesmannen gir kritikk etter at dement mann d\u00f8de -adressa.no", "Tok for lang tid", "- Har handlet forsvarlig"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "7a0fd1936996f82bf01c5517ab66a0696a183830"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Rennebu", "Demens"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Rennebu,Demens"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kommune", "handlet forsvarlig", "mann", "fylkesmannen", "dement mann", "mann d\u00f8de", "dement mann d\u00f8de"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["demens", "fylkesmannen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["rennebu", "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "tr\u00f8ndelag"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "solveig l\u00f8kken"}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11446349.ece/3vk0is/ALTERNATES/w980-default/20150820_212410.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value":